SNAILBot is a passive IRC logging bot written in Perl.
For more information and usage instructions, see the
homepage at http://www.jackgrigg.com/projects/snailbot

It is based on ilbot, whose homepage is
http://moritz.faui2k3.org/en/ilbot

The following new features have been added:
 * Multiple servers can be logged from a single instance.
 * Modular approach to including:
   * Analytics code, site counters etc.
   * Channel-specific links.
   * Channel-specific logos.
   * Channel-specific interactive usercount charts.
